ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisAppointment of VICKY EATRIDES of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a full-time member and Chairperson of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission, to hold office during good behavior for a term of five years, effective January 5, 2023.
